data.value:
The project ONION: Your Personal PlantCare Companion is a Windows Forms (WinForms) application developed in C#.NET with database connectivity, designed to assist plant owners in maintaining a consistent and effective care routine for their houseplants.
Many plant owners struggle with keeping track of watering schedules, sunlight exposure, and fertilization needs, leading to poor plant health. The previous console-based version lacked a graphical interface and persistent data storage. This new version will offer an interactive and user-friendly interface, with database-backed data management and automated reminders for plant care tasks.
